                        <interp inst="t18570105-name-132" type="given" value="MARY ANN"></interp>MARY ANN BOWYER</persName>
                  </hi>. I searched Mail at the station on 30th Dec.—I found on her a crown piece, which I gave the next day to the officer.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
