                  </hi>. These are both counterfeit, and from one mould. <hi rend="italic">Nicholls.</hi> When I ran, I ran across the road, because of the vehicles coming by.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18570105-name-134" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18570105-name-134" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
