                        <interp inst="t18570105-name-134" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE WATKINS</persName>
                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> No, he ran to get out of my way, and he got behind the <hi rend="italic">busses</hi>—he ran at least a hundred yards—he ran directly I took Mail—he still ran when he was on the other side of the way, till he was stopped by some gentleman—I did not lose sight of him—I was close at his heels.</p>
